WEBVTT

00:00:01.619 --> 00:00:05.761
For the past few years,
we've been calling men out.

00:00:07.103 --> 00:00:08.302
It had to be done.

00:00:08.326 --> 00:00:10.278
(Applause)

00:00:10.302 --> 00:00:15.646
But lately, I've been thinking
we need to do something even harder.

00:00:16.567 --> 00:00:20.149
We need, as my good friend
Tony Porter says,

00:00:20.173 --> 00:00:23.889
to find a way to call men in.

00:00:25.412 --> 00:00:29.420
My father began to sexually abuse me
when I was five years old.